      ],
      "description": "A large bag filled with multifaceted dice hangs from the Nightbane's wrist, belt, or other convenient point[cite: 7]. It is actually large and heavy enough to be used as a bludgeoning weapon in hand to hand combat[cite: 7].",
      "statModifiers": {
